    "In the investigation, we used a publicly available chest X-ray (CXR) dataset from Kaggle 57, 58.",
    "The same dataset has also been utilized in numerous other investigations.",
    "The dataset consists of three sections: train, test, and validation.",
    "Each section contains subfolders for Pneumonia and Normal CXRs.",
    "There are 5863 X-ray images in total as shown in Table 2."
